t;/a&gt;的硬件的强劲需求。该公司表示，截至 4 月份的财季销售额将达到 96 亿至 100 亿美元，而彭博社调查的分析师平均预期为 95.7 亿美元。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/upiWmOtFM5E5jiYslJO9r9LsXusg8P9dC9xotNYfRxjfQeNRN_Jptu8J7le_KF0Fs3tiOMlFR7pRLF9AmonctRmPn9oDfabSFvuzmlz85dYqDbbsp1KHr_PcqS-hXYRjj657iWpMWP5Fo7s3rMdRG7qRyV0Ui0k8mpLwuxdoNNa7s4my2gJi1Cypg0kxFzG1cW373XL6Gc0tBRr1mBp-pbMDuPXoW-jXDwN6bnibnUj5y_TGuhSxNAr_P1H1K9pIhGtoXNbcWV7Ee7vC-eUK9y6zcfsarrSB4Hsuanp3127WisFH6tST1HijJooYoFvwyhArIjuwLAN8GmPfHiLiaLU3q7XWjN2si3BllNOwm3-OSkyP3Z-z0ayGi1Ryr4VkbLNTEaELmLwgnVaoOzW49oA/YRfD3HpSJPzhKq3Ug_QRsK9m8BMlTgir/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3RnAlj9zGZk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3RnAlj9zGZk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt; Z 世代“金融虚无主义”向预测押注和加密货币致敬&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;财务上的“落后”正在促使人们转向高风险和投机性资产，以此作为迎头赶上的一种方式。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;联邦快递首次超越竞争对手联合包裹服务公司&lt;/strong&gt;，成为美国市值最大的包裹承运商，这是一个具有里程碑意义的时刻，突显了快递公司在不稳定的包裹递送业务中的不同路径。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这一里程碑&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/3uGOqmTVNPg9gEwv_QILMd_ithzy02flGkwyFbMPOorhen69NhXTofrqyDPcIz43ybzlwhGo6h7gbOOaNmyO3rSdxBHZTLVqy-YhiJA7naqYqXFAN4niFF7H8nZ63d0RWufbojJgIGQGLJdJjK-5YYFPU984PZAwsUsgrHPQl5T5w16ekeiBO9y9YVThlpW6WmFP5i_KRdrrLu15sFvUVpTIyPI2-4x4vm8xGmNmT8XHpJ1-rS775Rgqut1MbUbi6NMywxiVAra5E41B_O989pzKSo9xU-1nj4fhVOkMWvjMTtGojQvIs69cr3FGwI-5bMuQWCMuenufAGJ4Pgb6txbXrmr0C7x4GojtLxevhgScM_1olpUNC_7EJFIgYWENQslUFAxlNy4jZrG6vUs_FyEmbaB1N_mu5Vr2Zc2yoV4KwUr5Pa90FVt5XUJu9QrTVHjaRrJ9BlXWoQmvB4pTiffx2q9RurTilp7CaTTmpE_W49LtaQD2dHKkwmZFG5LzsU0q/cPfO5uMjsBwgJWxp0vENPMR8xHexliso/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="联邦快递市值超越 UPS，成为美国最大包裹公司"&gt;标志着 UPS 股价多年来的下滑&lt;/a&gt;，该公司面临着劳动力成本、销量下降以及与亚马逊关系质疑的压力。对于联邦快递来说，这是管理层通过削减成本、提高利润和剥离货运业务的计划赢得投资者支持的最新迹象。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Ngx4qhQ3ZG5x-qe6_wCL2hjjua7hG2XslYbjTJOFcMU-Zwr4Sj1cMC409In1JpTPfw26ls9NyJj81IZmsmp4wNUy2akRAIb80W2f7IpvmdNEgKqqsWZXBwuhAcvyuA75xj4ZRwhGfkrndbeMTVGg1IXcYszdB7_fN0Pesjdhjx1fch6B2VO8Q2ObWoopwRFEKiaxmsrpC4p4Xon122HYibeQLC10AuPnAdlLu2__ZlLL9_MgnVTPJU-cW_2Eg2UrEoXGkUm2CRAw334iKjzbQDhSBH04n9sPGJEFftJT-EAMYvb1eaUWq045MsTsx6JdAthzO9GaGTOFNqKmjYRl7nqXiFjwhoMmoFZjOBHgJbTH2KyV11dgB3lcJtRkAYpg8ccz3_CjF2_h7cn5uz46/Tc39byAaoMJ7agIxxUAGMArBYJW_dItO/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iobSkiziroA8/v26/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Adam Lundin, chairman of Lundin Mining Corp., left, and Jack Lundin, chief executive officer of Lundin Mining Corp., at the Lundin Group offices in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Tuesday Sept. 10, 2024. To build a copper mining d